export default function CustomPadding(){ return( <>

Excellent Custom Padding for Fabrics Enhancing Support and Longevity

Testfabrics, Inc. ensures that its custom fabric padding service meets the distinctive needs of every industry whether it's upholstery, specialty textiles, or garments. Our exceptional padding enhances the durability, comfort, and longevity of fabrics. We use premium-quality materials and state-of-the-art techniques to provide optimal lining and cushioning for every fabric, making us stand out among service providers.


General Lab Padding Equipment Features:

  • 6-14" workable fabric widths possible, inventory or client-supplied
  • 1-liter capacity stainless steel 'dip' pan
  • 10-liter capacity stainless steel gravity-fed supply tank
  • Wet-pick up adjustable, via air pressure, 5.5" diameter
  • Rubber-coated rollers
  • Air circulating drying oven, temperatures from 75F to 475F
  • Approximate 6-meter total fabric length, from let-off to take-up
  • Variable speed control, pressure rollers, and take-up synchronized
  • Post-cutting and sampling available

Have your Next Small-width Padding Trial with Us! Reach out for Further Information
